subject: Mixed Martial Arts
lead_paragraph: McGregor dropped Jose Aldo 13 seconds into their U.F.C. featherweight title match. Luke Rockhold won the middleweight title by beating Chris Weidman.
snippet: McGregor dropped Jose Aldo 13 seconds into their U.F.C. featherweight title match. Luke Rockhold won the middleweight title by beating Chris Weidman.
